About Hastings Ranch and Farm
Southern-Inspired Style and Elegance in Every Event
Welcome to our family-owned ranch in St. Cloud, Florida, where farming meets fun on 220 acres of countryside bliss.
We’re George and Debbie Hastings, the proud owners of this beautiful ranch and farm. Our journey began with a dream—a dream of having a place of our own where we could raise cattle, cultivate our own food, and create a safe haven for our beloved grandchildren to play. After a search that led us far and wide, we stumbled upon untouched land that felt like destiny. Nestled among the picturesque landscapes were magnificent oak trees, offering their timeless shade and serene beauty.
Today, our farm stands as a testament to the enduring spirit of family, community, and the joy of the outdoors. It’s a place where family values meet nature’s bounty. Here at our ranch, we’ve cultivated more than just crops; we’ve nurtured unforgettable family memories.
Whether you’re seeking adventure, tranquility, or a taste of the simple life, our family-owned ranch in St. Cloud is the perfect destination. We look forward to sharing the warmth and hospitality of our farm with you and your family. Come and experience the magic of our ranch, where every visit feels like coming home.
